import React, { Component } from "react"; export default class FormPacients extends Component{ state = { nome: "", peso: 0, altura: 0, gorduraCorporal: 0 } alterarInput = (e) => ( this.setState({ ...this.state, nome: e.target.value }) ) render(){ return(
this.setState(e)} placeholder="Nome:" value={this.state.nome}/>
) } }
